reviewText: My granddaughter loves Baby First.  Keeps her entertained on long car rides.
Good starter video for babies - newborn to 4

I was  hoping for a version of what I see on a half hour of programming variety on Baby First TV.  This is not the best version or representation of the show.  The show holds attention of child, this dvd does not.
Bought these Baby First videos for my grandson.  He loves them!
